Label: util_TNC Single - Cost
Expression: @np.maximum(TNC_single_baseFare*2 + (df.s2_dist_skims_out + df.s2_dist_skims_inb) * TNC_single_costPerMile + (df.s2_time_skims_out + df.s2_time_skims_inb) * TNC_single_costPerMinute, TNC_single_costMinimum*2)*100 + df.s2_cost_skims_out + df.s2_cost_skims_inb

Label: util_TNC Shared - Cost
Expression: @np.maximum(TNC_shared_baseFare*2 + (df.s2_dist_skims_out + df.s2_dist_skims_inb) * TNC_shared_costPerMile + (df.s2_time_skims_out + df.s2_time_skims_inb)* TNC_shared_costPerMinute, TNC_shared_costMinimum*2)*100 + df.s2_cost_skims_out + df.s2_cost_skims_inb
